buyerAgent.name: Mary Bartos and The Bartos Group

data.description: Welcome to this peaceful waterfront retreat featuring 2 beds, 2 baths, a bonus den space and a convenient attached 2-car garage. The open-concept layout is accentuated by high ceilings, elegant plantation shutters, and recessed lighting. Step onto the expansive screened lanai and discover your own personal sanctuary, complete with a private pool and a covered seating area perfect for outdoor dining and entertaining guests. Imagine unwinding or enjoying your evening drink while admiring a picturesque lakefront sunset with your southern exposure. This villa is nestled in the quiet rear section of the community, ensuring tranquility and freedom from road noise. As a resident of the Verona Walk community, you'll have access to a wide array of amenities, including a 24/7 guarded entrance, basketball, pickleball, billiards, beauty salon, post office, gas station, clubhouse, pool,  fitness center, library, bocce, dining, and tennis. This home is your gateway to the desirable Naples lifestyle you've always dreamed of. Whether you're looking for a permanent residence or a vacation getaway, don't miss the opportunity to own a piece of paradise!
